<br>
<br>
<br>
Maybe it's just me, but I've used the description that the game designers left as a basic guide for my character.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
OOC, I think that Tier'Dal ladies are quite cute.  And many of them are absolutely wonderful roleplayers, from my experiences with them (and they're usually antagonistic towards me, which I expect from them).<br>
<br>
IC, I'd like to see them all spitted on pikes and displayed around their hometown, just for effect...<br>
<br>
The fact that a Tier'Dal was upset at seeing you and your husband together is just the tip of the iceberg, in my humble opinion - there are a lot of Fier'Dal that would have similar reactions.  And most likely that person was simply reacting according to the racial hatred that exists between Fier'Dal and Tier'Dal - it was nothing personal towards you, the player.  I get the creeps every time I see Seraphimm (Koda'Dal) hanging out with Rebelle,  but I simply look at her as a &quot;fallen angel&quot;, for lack of a better description.  How each character reacts is different, just like in real life.  But I'm certain it was nothing personal to you, the player.<br>
<br>
But that's just my 2 copper's worth...<br>
